# Employee Management System (Java)

This is a simple console-based Java application that allows users to:
✔ Add Employee  
✔ View All Employees  
✔ Search Employee by ID  
✔ Delete Employee  

### Technologies Used
- Core Java
- OOP Principles (Class, Object, Encapsulation)
- ArrayList for Data Storage
- Scanner for User Input

### Purpose
This project demonstrates hands-on Java knowledge in real-world applications.

### How to Run
1️⃣ Compile the file  
   → `javac EmployeeManagementSystem.java`  
2️⃣ Run the program  
   → `java EmployeeManagementSystem`

